metadata.name: Nakamoto Geometry
metadata.description: The ENCRYPTO 21 collection involves the magic of the 21 million Bitcoins to come to life, involves the white paper as the basis of a new entity of financial life, summoning freedom, security, and certainty; this work detonates the second sample of Mr. Blockchain as a lover of time and design, summoning art, purity and the recognition of man as a " zoon politikon" but also as a libertarian of the future.
